Hey guys lets do something fun!!! WIN MY 1976 MARTIN acoustic for only $25!! This guitar has been on damn near every record we have made. And also in the “Waitin around to die” video. All you have to do to enter is click the paypal link on my profile page and send the $25 through FRIENDS AND FAMILY and make sure and include your Full name and preferred email address in the notes. When all 300 spots are sold i will draw a winner live right here on Instagram. It would sure make a great Christmas gift. Of course I will pay for the shipping cost and even sign it if you would like. Good luck and see ya out on the road soon!!! 🔥🔥🍺🍺
Ok guys thats it!!! Sold out quick. Thanks so much and i will keep you posted on the drawing next Saturday!!

Ok guys here are all the names for the Martin contest. Keep in mind some of you used business accounts so look for those names. I will get them all cut up and post the drawing tomorrow at 3pm eastern, 2pm Central, 1pm Mountain and Noon on the West Coast. Good luck and see you tomorrow!!

Christopher Young!!! Come on down!! You are the proud new owner of this 1976 Martin. There are a few of you that spent a lot of money on these tickets and I didn’t forget you.
